archimate:BusinessObject.name: Acquired system
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: The system or system element (product or service) is delivered to the acquirer from a supplier consistent with the delivery conditions of the acquisition agreement

properties.value: Ein beschafftes System (Produkt oder Dienstleistung) ist eine vom Zulieferer an den Beschaffer gemäß den Lieferbedingungen des Beschaffungsvertrages ausgeliefertes System oder Systemelement.
The system or system element (product or service) is delivered to the acquirer from a supplier consistent with the delivery conditions of the acquisition agreement
